## Datasets

### ISIC Challenge Dataset
- Source: https://challenge.isic-archive.com/data/#milk10k
- Description: Dermoscopic skin lesion images used for training and evaluation.
- Notes: Publicly available for download.

### Hugging Face Synthetic EHR Dataset
- Source: https://huggingface.co/datasets/electricsheepafrica/Africa-skin-cancer-images-EHR/viewer/default/train
- Description: Synthetic African-focused electronic health record dataset used to improve representation of darker skin tones.
- Notes: Publicly available via Hugging Face datasets.
